title: Snaps - Quinn Ewers & Texas playoff bound? Is Heisman CJ Stroud's to lose? Alabama-Tennessee preview
itunes:title: Snaps - Quinn Ewers & Texas playoff bound? Is Heisman CJ Stroud's to lose? Alabama-Tennessee preview
description:
Aaron Murray and T-Bob Hebert discuss if Texas can become the first two-loss team to make the college football playoff with Quinn Ewers back. They later debate if the Heisman Trophy is CJ Stroud's to lose and are joined by former Tennessee Volunteers' quarterback and host of "The Erik Ainge Show" Erik Ainge to discuss Tennessee's top 10 showdown with Nick Saban and Alabama. #Volume #ColinCowherd #Herd
